# ============================================================================
# DropSafe .gitignore
# AI-Powered Parametric Income Insurance Platform
# ============================================================================
#
# SECURITY FIRST: This file prevents sensitive data, build artifacts,
# and unnecessary files from being accidentally committed to git.
#
# ⚠️ CRITICAL RULES:
# 1. NEVER commit .env files (only .env.example)
# 2. NEVER commit API keys, tokens, or credentials
# 3. NEVER commit personal backup files or databases
# 4. ALWAYS keep .env.example (it's the template with no secrets)
# 5. ALWAYS keep supabase/*.sql migration files (infrastructure as code)
#
# ============================================================================

# ============================================================================
# SECTION 1: ENVIRONMENT & SECRETS (CRITICAL!)
# ============================================================================
# These contain API keys, database passwords, and authentication tokens
# If you accidentally commit these, IMMEDIATELY rotate all keys!

